# Database (PostgreSQL only)
#
# Railway ichida: Postgres plugin `DATABASE_URL` (private) odatda backend service ga ulanadi.
#
# Lokal mashina (npm run dev): private host ishlamaydi. Quyidagidan bittasi:
# 1) Postgres service → Variables → `DATABASE_PUBLIC_URL` yoki TCP proxy:
#    RAILWAY_TCP_PROXY_DOMAIN=...
#    RAILWAY_TCP_PROXY_PORT=...   (ko‘pincha 5432 emas — UI dagi qiymat)
#    POSTGRES_USER / POSTGRES_PASSWORD / POSTGRES_DB
# 2) Yoki bitta qator: DATABASE_PUBLIC_URL=postgresql://...@host:port/db?sslmode=require
#
# URL da `sslmode` bo‘lmasa: `POSTGRES_SSLMODE=require` (masalan, tashqi TCP proxy).
# Kod `*.proxy.rlwy.net` host uchun sslmode=require ni avtomatik qo‘shadi.
#
# Docker (ixtiyoriy): repo ildizida `docker compose --profile postgres up -d`
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@127.0.0.1:5432/swift_bookings
#
# Homebrew Postgres (macOS): `brew install postgresql@16` → `brew services start postgresql@16`
# Bir marta: `npm run db:local:reset --prefix django_backend` (DB + bootstrap + migrate + seed)
# Faqat xonalar: `npm run db:seed --prefix django_backend`
# yoki alohida:
# POSTGRES_HOST=127.0.0.1
# POSTGRES_PORT=5432
# POSTGRES_DB=swift_bookings
# POSTGRES_USER=postgres
# POSTGRES_PASSWORD=postgres
# POSTGRES_SSLMODE=prefer
# Production tavsiya:
# DJANGO_DEBUG=0
# DJANGO_SECRET_KEY=<uzun-random-secret>
# DJANGO_ALLOWED_HOSTS=*.up.railway.app
# DJANGO_SECURE_SSL_REDIRECT=1
# RAILWAY_PUBLIC_DOMAIN=<auto railway domain>

# Telegram bot (faqat serverda; Mini App frontendda token bo'lmaydi)
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=

# ngrok public tunnel (https://dashboard.ngrok.com/get-started/your-authtoken)
# NGROK_AUTHTOKEN=

# Passport/ID OCR: PassportEye (MRZ) + zaxira Tesseract. Tizimda: brew install tesseract tesseract-lang
# TESSERACT_CMD=/opt/homebrew/bin/tesseract
# TESSERACT_LANGS=eng+rus
# MRZ uchun legacy tessdata: PASSPORTEYE_TESSERACT_PARAMS=--oem 0

# OpenAI hujjat parser (birinchi yuklangan hujjat rasmi)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_DOC_PARSER_MODEL=gpt-5.4
